revisions.description: This is the tenth revision of VMware vRealize Network Insight Manager SNMP notifications. It adds fifty two new notifications, see vmwNetworkInsightNotificationGroup10.
This is the ninth revision of VMware vRealize Network Insight Manager SNMP notifications. It adds two new notifications, see vmwNetworkInsightNotificationGroup9.
This is the eighth revision of VMware vRealize Network Insight Manager SNMP notifications. It adds two new notifications, see vmwNetworkInsightNotificationGroup8.
This is the seventh revision of VMware vRealize Network Insight Manager SNMP notifications. It adds seventeen new notifications, see vmwNetworkInsightNotificationGroup7.
This is the sixth revision of VMware vRealize Network Insight Manager SNMP notifications. It adds fourteen new notifications, see vmwNetworkInsightNotificationGroup6.

This is the fifth revision of VMware vRealize Network Insight Manager SNMP notifications. This revision introduces below changes, some of which are non backward compatible. a. All event notifications have their varbind contents changed from : OBJECTS { vmwAffectedObject, vmwEventSeverity, vmwVrniUrl, vmwTimestamp, vmwOperatorDesc, vmwEventName} to : OBJECTS { vmwEventSeverity, vmwAffectedObject, vmwOperatorDesc, vmwVrniUrl, vmwTimestamp, vmwEventName } b. Syntax changes for TC - VmwVrniSeverity was { cleared(0), info(1), major(2) } is now VmwVrniSeverity {Critical, Moderate, Warning, Info and CLEARED} c. Support for new events added, see vmwNetworkInsightNotificationGroup5
This is the fourth revision of VMware vRealize Network Insight Manager SNMP notifications. It adds fourteen new notifications, see vmwNetworkInsightNotificationGroup4.
This is the third revision of VMware vRealize Network Insight Manager SNMP notifications. This version added nineteen new notifications, see vmwNetworkInsightNotificationGroup3 for complete listing.

This is the second revision of VMware vRealize Network Insight Manager SNMP notifications. It introduces new notifications, see vmwNetworkInsightNotificationGroup2, and updates existing notifications to append the vmwEventName managed object.
This is the first revision of VMware vRealize Network Insight Manager SNMP notifications.
